Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leucocyte计划好像很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透明的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢这种恶趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你安插进去的钉子怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成败对半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔戈先生 集先生 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这次跟涯一起吧 京
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以一起战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾不能看你们进行演习战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 集先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连那么小的孩子都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有自信的人果然是能够一呼百应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的事要是我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没人响应我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世上到头来还是偏爱那些自以为是的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还完全不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就凭你这水平以后也不见得能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个姑且不谈 你刚才说的中伤了涯和我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Void那东西从谁那都能提取出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么努力 弄得跟真想加入这里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:52.44,isong_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}風がなびいた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:52.44,isong_sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}随风漂泊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:10:01.15,isong_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}二つ重なって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:10:01.15,isong_sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:11.08,isong_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}生きた証を 私は謳おう 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:11.08,isong_sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}我来歌颂 逝去生命的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:23.57,isong_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}名もなきイエローの雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:23.57,isong_sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}这无名的金黄色的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟第一次遇到你时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈为什么在葬仪社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么来这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最主要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为了我而赶来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 祈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如… 我是说假如
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你一起离开葬仪社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯给我取了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给一无所有的我取了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给了我这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那「属于我的」「在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些话都是什么…意…思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为涯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈小姐 等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么 就我一个人擅自误会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都觉得涯好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走路不长眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你乱看什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看那个房间了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢祈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你可要节哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他俩每个月会有两三次晚上一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家装作没看见 但应该都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫瀬你没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是喜欢涯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么喜欢啊 我是尊敬涯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她觉得涯好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来 只是女孩子对好强长相又帅的男人没什么免疫力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还小 什么都不了解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想了解的话 就先赢下明天的演习战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢了你就能正式加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样你肯定有很多新的发现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定不要别人帮助了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但自己爬上去的姿势有点不太优雅 所以不想让人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能回避下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越像那个女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个中队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟预想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OAU还有Leave Nations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一群规规矩矩的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演习战现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以攻取Leucocyte的作战方案D-14为蓝本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,场景设定是你必须独自应对End Rave
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能穿过斯坦纳 跑到我身后的车内 就算你赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被颜料弹击中会晕过去的 集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也太乱来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也躲不过绫瀬的End Rave
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上斯坦纳越来越快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫姐 可以连接了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么Ready——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背对着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃得可真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然徒手对付ER太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再发呆可是会死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 怎么做才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔戈先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我作弊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你只是使用了你自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗骑士…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的那么阴郁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你 集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起你就是我们的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给 奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的东西下次可别弄丢了 好好保管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在玩伙伴游戏吗 好像很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,研二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,研二？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城户研二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你从第四隔离区救出的那个人 集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴游戏是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点松散呢 各方面都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯那家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leucocyte刚对Delta Point射击了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯在的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输入功率3%发射完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标被破坏率110%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,误差0.7米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}注：出自《神曲》地狱篇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过我 进入万劫不复之人群
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汝等入此地 抛弃一切希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:26.65,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}もうあなたから愛されることも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:26.65,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}已经不再被你爱护着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:33.32,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}必要とされることもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:33.32,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}也不再被你所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:39.96,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}そして私は　こうして一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:39.96,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}我就这样 独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.40,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.40,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:49.93,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}あの時あなたはなんて言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:49.93,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}那时的你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:56.62,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}届かない言葉は宙を舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:56.62,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}无法传达的言语早已飘逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:03.29,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}分かってるのに　今日もしてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:03.29,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}虽然心里明白  却又一如从前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:09.93,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}叶わぬ 願いことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:09.93,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}许下那  无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:16.64,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}はなさないで　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:16.64,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}请不要放手 紧紧地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:20.02,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}手を握ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:20.02,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:26.86,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}あなたと二人つづくと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:26.86,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}说好了两人将携手同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:35.85,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}繋いだ　その手は暖かくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:35.85,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}牵着我的那双手是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:43.97,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}優しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:43.97,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}如此柔和